snippet.title: Galaxy Tactics - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter a world of tactical mayhem, with dozens of unique weapons to obliterate your opponents, on an everchanging battlefield with destructible terrain! Manage your arsenal and unleash epic and game-changing combos, online and offline, solo or with friends, and become the greatest in the galaxy!

Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3574210/Galaxy_Tactics
